title: Fright Night - Choose Your Own Adventure 164.pdf
description:
Here is Fright Night, by Edward Packard and illustrated by Frank Bolle, "Choose Your Own Adventure" #164

Published by Bantam Books, October 1995

This used to be a school library book, so there are some stamps inside the book indicating so.  Also this book has taken some water damaged, and you can see it on all the pages after about p80, but it's not too big a deal.

Enjoy
